r that it would be delivered by the end of this month. In fact, during our =
weekly ideas meeting, my partner <b>Tara Palmeri </b>and I had discussed ho=
w to address the fact that the verdict would likely be descending at the <i=
>very moment </i>that her dispatch for
The Best &amp; The Brightest would land in subscribers=E2=80=99 inboxes. In=
